Put all the driver files (correct.php, createphar.php, getcontents.php) and run-tests.sh script in src/sapi/cli folder
Set the value of variable phar.readonly = False in php.ini-development file and 
copy php.ini-development file to /usr/local/lib/php.ini.

Execute the run-tests.sh script using command: bash run-tests.sh 

 
